fields.value: Bureau of Economic Analysis (BEA) Regional Economic Program 1987-

dsDescriptionValue.value: "BEA's regional economics program provides estimates, analyses, and projections by region, State, metropolitan area and county. The program makes the following data available: personal income and wage and salary disbursements; annual State disposable personal income and personal tax and nontax payments; annual State full- and part-time wage and salary employment; annual State and county personal income, transfer payments, and farm income and expenses; and annual State and county full- and par t-time total employment."
